sequenceDiagram
    %% --- Tag Management: Create Tag ---
    participant User
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BE as Backend
    participant PG as PostgreSQL

    User->>FE: Submit new tag (create)
    FE->>BE: POST /tags (with tag name)
    BE->>PG: Insert new Tag (if not exists)
    BE-->>FE: Return created tag
    FE-->>User: Show tag available for assignment

    %% --- Tag Management: Assign Tag to Resource ---
    User->>FE: Assign existing tag to resource
    FE->>BE: POST /resources/{id}/tags (with tag id)
    BE->>PG: Create LearningResourceTag link
    BE-->>FE: Confirm tag assignment
    FE-->>User: Show updated tags on resource
